<paragraph id="8B4936A5161EFFA0FF79F9BDFE96FCDF" blockId="10.[151,1436,1560,1973]" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis id="B982EAB7161EFFA0FF79F9BDFD0FFC4A" bold="true" box="[197,732,1560,1586]" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">
Female genitalia (based on 
<specimenCount id="9DF0FD2C161EFFA0FD98F9BDFD1CFC4A" box="[548,719,1560,1586]" pageId="10" pageNumber="53" type="generic" typeStatus="paratype">one paratype</specimenCount>
).
</emphasis>
Sternite VII (
<figureCitation id="13CD2A20161EFFA0FC3AF9BCFC0DFC4B" box="[902,990,1561,1587]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–38" captionStartId="10.[151,270,1450,1474]" captionTargetBox="[160,1421,515,1399]" captionTargetId="figure-292@10.[151,1436,506,1426]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 36–38. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov., female paratype: (36) sternite VII, ventral view; (37) pygofer, lateral view; (38) second valvula, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321370" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321370/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">Fig. 36</figureCitation>
) broader than long; posterior margin with three distinct lobes; lateral margins approximately rectilinear and parallel; surface with small setae mostly on posterior portion. Pygofer (
<figureCitation id="13CD2A20161EFFA0FDD5F9C3FD10FCF8" box="[617,707,1638,1664]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–38" captionStartId="10.[151,270,1450,1474]" captionTargetBox="[160,1421,515,1399]" captionTargetId="figure-292@10.[151,1436,506,1426]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 36–38. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov., female paratype: (36) sternite VII, ventral view; (37) pygofer, lateral view; (38) second valvula, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321370" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321370/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">Fig. 37</figureCitation>
) as in 
<taxonomicName id="4CF64D26161EFFA0FCABF9C3FC3BFC07" box="[791,1000,1638,1663]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Exogonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavomaculata">
<emphasis id="B982EAB7161EFFA0FCABF9C3FC3BFC07" box="[791,1000,1638,1663]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">E. flavomaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Second valvulae (
<figureCitation id="13CD2A20161EFFA0FB68F9C3FAFDFCF8" box="[1236,1326,1638,1664]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–38" captionStartId="10.[151,270,1450,1474]" captionTargetBox="[160,1421,515,1399]" captionTargetId="figure-292@10.[151,1436,506,1426]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 36–38. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov., female paratype: (36) sternite VII, ventral view; (37) pygofer, lateral view; (38) second valvula, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321370" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321370/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">Fig. 38</figureCitation>
) as in 
<taxonomicName id="4CF64D26161EFFA0FA3EF9C3FEECFCDE" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Exogonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavomaculata">
<emphasis id="B982EAB7161EFFA0FA3EF9C3FEECFCDE" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">E. flavomaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
